---
layout: "layouts/base.njk"
title: "Shop — Digital Resources & Premium Readings"
description: "Chinese zodiac digital products, BaZi starter kits, feng shui guides, and premium personalized readings."
keywords: "Chinese zodiac shop, BaZi reading, feng shui guide, zodiac forecast, premium reading"
ogType: "website"
shopSchema: true
permalink: "/shop/"
breadcrumbs:
  - label: "Home"
    url: "/"
  - label: "Shop"
faq:
  - q: "What format are the digital products in?"
    a: "All digital products are delivered as PDF files that can be viewed on any device — computer, tablet, or phone. Some products also include supplementary worksheets or reference charts as separate PDFs."
  - q: "How do I access my purchase after buying?"
    a: "After completing your purchase through Gumroad, you will receive an email with a download link. You can also access your purchases at any time through your Gumroad library. The download link does not expire."
  - q: "What is your refund policy?"
    a: "We offer a 30-day refund policy on all digital products. If you are unsatisfied for any reason, contact us and we will process a full refund. For premium readings, please see the premium readings FAQ for specific terms."
  - q: "Is my payment information secure?"
    a: "All payments are processed securely through PayPal (for premium readings) or Gumroad (for digital products). We never store your credit card information. Both platforms use industry-standard encryption and are PCI DSS compliant."
---
{% include "partials/breadcrumbs.njk" %}

<div class="lang-en">
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-content">
    <span class="overline">Resources</span>
    <h1>Shop</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Digital guides, forecasts, and personalized readings rooted in classical Chinese metaphysical traditions.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="article-layout">
  <article class="article-content">

    <section class="shop-section" id="readings">
      <h2>Premium Personalized Readings</h2>
      <p>Our practitioners prepare detailed BaZi and zodiac reports using classical methodology — each one individually crafted for your birth data.</p>

      <div class="shop-readings-preview">
        {%- for item in shop.premiumReadings %}
        <div class="shop-reading-card{% if item.featured %} shop-reading-card--featured{% endif %}">
          <h3>{{ item.name }}</h3>
          <div class="pricing-amount"><span class="pricing-currency">$</span>{{ item.price }}</div>
          <p>{{ item.description }}</p>
          <div class="pricing-delivery">Delivery: {{ item.delivery }}</div>
          <a href="/premium-readings/" class="btn {% if item.featured %}btn-gold{% else %}btn-outline{% endif %} btn-sm">Learn More</a>
        </div>
        {%- endfor %}
      </div>

      <p style="text-align:center;margin-top:var(--sp-lg)"><a href="/premium-readings/" class="btn btn-primary">View All Reading Options &rarr;</a></p>
    </section>

    <hr class="gold-rule">

    <section class="shop-section" id="products">
      <h2>Digital Products</h2>
      <p>Downloadable guides, forecasts, and workbooks to deepen your understanding of Chinese astrology and metaphysics.</p>

      <div class="shop-filters">
        <button class="shop-filter-btn active" data-filter="all">All</button>
        <button class="shop-filter-btn" data-filter="forecasts">Forecasts</button>
        <button class="shop-filter-btn" data-filter="guides">Guides</button>
        <button class="shop-filter-btn" data-filter="education">Education</button>
        <button class="shop-filter-btn" data-filter="calendars">Calendars</button>
      </div>

      <div class="shop-products-grid">
        {%- for item in shop.digitalProducts %}
        <div class="product-card{% if item.featured %} product-card--featured{% endif %}" data-category="{{ item.category }}">
          <h3>{{ item.name }}</h3>
          <p class="product-subtitle">{{ item.subtitle }}</p>
          <ul class="product-features">
            {%- for feature in item.features %}
            <li>{{ feature }}</li>
            {%- endfor %}
          </ul>
          <div class="product-footer">
            <span class="product-price">${{ item.price }}</span>
            <a href="{{ item.gumroadUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-gold btn-sm">Buy Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        {%- endfor %}
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="gold-rule">

    <section id="faq">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-section">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">What format are the digital products in?</button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>All digital products are delivered as PDF files that can be viewed on any device — computer, tablet, or phone. Some products also include supplementary worksheets or reference charts as separate PDFs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">How do I access my purchase after buying?</button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>After completing your purchase through Gumroad, you will receive an email with a download link. You can also access your purchases at any time through your Gumroad library. The download link does not expire.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">What is your refund policy?</button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We offer a 30-day refund policy on all digital products. If you are unsatisfied for any reason, contact us and we will process a full refund. For premium readings, please see the <a href="/premium-readings/#faq">premium readings FAQ</a> for specific terms.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">Is my payment information secure?</button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>All payments are processed securely through PayPal (for premium readings) or Gumroad (for digital products). We never store your credit card information. Both platforms use industry-standard encryption and are PCI DSS compliant.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </article>
</div>
</div>

